      <title>美元成为本周市场混乱的最新受害者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/dollar-emerges-as-latest-victim-of-this-week-s-markets-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球贸易战风险破坏了美国经济增长，因此美元成为本周市场动荡的最新受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/dollar-emerges-as-latest-victim-of-this-week-s-markets-mayhem</guid>
