    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔的日元债券交易是有史以来最小的贸易战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/berkshire-sells-628-million-in-yen-bonds-in-smallest-japan-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）周五在周五的日元交易中出售了900亿日元（6.28亿美元）的债券，这是由于贸易战不断升级的市场动荡而有史以来最小的日元交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/berkshire-sells-628-million-in-yen-bonds-in-smallest-japan-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 00:59:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税动荡火花攀登以录制时，黄金“最佳地点”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/gold-hits-record-as-recession-anxiety-has-traders-seeking-havens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于关税对全球经济的影响的担忧使投资者推向了避风港，黄金上升到每盎司3,200美元以上的创纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/gold-hits-record-as-recession-anxiety-has-traders-seeking-havens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:57:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票延长下降，美元落在关税困境上：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和债券在三年来最大的暴跌后，股票和债券恢复了抛售，由于全球贸易战争恶化，股票损失损失，这已经侵蚀了已经脆弱的风险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
